channel.title: Webclient Needed for - DragonGuild RS Look-Alike Server
channel.description:
I need someone to build me a webclient. My server is a RuneScape Look-Alike. It is finally completed. I have been working on this now for about 2 years. Dialouge is updates. If you can build me a webclient for it, I will make you administrator and Rep++. My servers name is: DragonGuild.
A little bit about myself:
I came here from Xele Ltd. because they asked me to create a webclient and if I needed help then I had permission to ask and identify myself and also give rewards. If you can create a webclient for me that would be awesome.
You can also create a background for this. I want it to be professional. If you need anything post here. Thanks.
